<FIRST>a a AM-ReligionRoundup Adv21   04-19 0567</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Religion Roundup, Adv 21,0588</SECOND>
<HEAD>$adv21</HEAD>
<HEAD>For Release Friday AMs, April 21, or Thereafter</HEAD>
<DATELINE>INDIANAPOLIS (AP) </DATELINE>
